data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2-story, 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse nestled in the desirable Ruskin community of Florida. With its prime location near I-75 and US 41, this townhouse offers convenient access to transportation routes, schools, shops, and plenty of recreational options, including the Apollo Beach Preserve and nearby parks.This 2021 townhouse offers modern amenities such as shaker style white cabinets with soft close mechanism. Kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, combined with granite counter tops providing a stylish and functional space for culinary endeavors. A washer and dryer are also included for your convenience. The townhouse boasts a well-designed layout, with a garden tub in the master bathroom for relaxation and a spacious master closet to accommodate your wardrobe.  The backyard is fenced, ensuring privacy and providing a safe area for outdoor activities. Exterior features include hurricane shutters, providing added protection during stormy weather conditions. Community amenities include a refreshing pool within walking distance, perfect for enjoying sunny Florida days. Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhouse your new home. It offers a blend of comfort, convenience, and modern living in a highly sought-after location.Assumable mortgage to qualified buyers through Freedom Mortgage, call for more details.
